<br><center><h1>Mohs Hardness Scale</h1><br>
<h4>A rapid hardness test for field and classroom use</h4>
<br><h4>Article by:  <a rel=3D"author" href=3D"https://geology.com/authors/=
hobart-king/">Hobart M. King</a>, PhD</h4>
</center><br><br></div>


<section>

