>
<p class=3D"caption"><b>Mohs Hardness Kit:</b> A Mohs Hardness Scale kit co=
ntaining: (1) talc; (2) gypsum; (3) calcite; (4) fluorite; (5) apatite; (6)=
 orthoclase; (7) quartz; (8) topaz; and (9) corundum. Diamond (10) is not i=
ncluded in most kits to keep the cost down. Also, a diamond specimen would =
be so small that it would need to be mounted in a handle to be useful. You =
can find Mohs Hardness Kits in the <a href=3D"https://geology.com/store/col=
lections/hardness-kit.shtml">Geology.com Store</a>.</p>
